  <body>
    <p><b>POD documents</b> are differentiated from <xref href="topic_trees.dita">Topic Tree
        documents</xref> by having <sourcexml>comm:body/level/@leveltype="landingpage"</sourcexml>.
      Any landing page source document with this mark-up is converted according to the instructions
      provided in this subsection of this CI document.</p>
    <note>The above mark-up indicates what <b><u>differentiates</u></b> landing pages that are POD
      documents from landing pages that are Topic Tree documents. <b><u>Both</u></b> POD documents
          <b><u>and</u></b> Topic Tree documents will also have a
        <sourcexml>docinfo:selector</sourcexml> that <b><u>starts</u></b> with the exact text
      "LandingPages_" (including the underscore), as described at the <xref href="body.dita">beginning of this Body section</xref>.</note>
    <section>
      <title>Source XML showing indication of a POD document</title>
      <codeblock>

&lt;COMMENTARYDOC ...&gt;
  &lt;docinfo ...&gt;
    &lt;!-- ... --&gt;
    &lt;docinfo:selector&gt;LandingPages_News Analysis&lt;/docinfo:selector&gt;
    &lt;!-- ... --&gt;
  &lt;/docinfo&gt;
  &lt;comm:body&gt;
    &lt;level leveltype="landingpage"&gt;
    &lt;!-- ... --&gt;

      </codeblock>
    </section>
